:name:
Synergy (ability)

:coretxt:
Choose one ability. 
You are extremely comfortable when using this ability.
You are learned to use it with such ease that yo can combine it with other ability when they are able to support each other.
Whenever you are able to use this ability and some other ability you can add weaker as bonus dice.
If one ability might only aid and other is clearly primary ability, you can still add secondary abilty as bonus dice.
You can learn synergy multiple times but you can never add bonus dice from several abilities.

:cost:
1 from related pool

:tags:
Universal
